The paper proposes a coding scheme based on interference alignment and interference decoding, which are techniques used in signal processing and communication systems (cs.SI). The paper also mentions the use of feedback to improve the performance of the network, which is a topic in control engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the paper discusses the number of generalized degrees of freedom, which is a concept used in multi-user communication systems (cs.MM).
